abstract: With a series of retweets, President Trump kept up attacks on federal law enforcement agencies, despite pleas from the attorney general.
snippet: With a series of retweets, President Trump kept up attacks on federal law enforcement agencies, despite pleas from the attorney general.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Ignoring appeals from his attorney general to stop tweeting about the Justice Department, President Trump renewed his attacks on the agency on Wednesday, demanding “JUSTICE” for himself and all future presidents.
